DESK BLINGOTRON 3000 commands

triggerword command arg1 arg2 arg3

off - turn me off :-(

color R G B - solid color in rgb, ie RGB 255 0 0 is red

fade R G B [t] - fade to this color with a delay/change of [t], which is optional (default is 20)

pulse R1 G1 B1 R2 G2 B2 [t] - pulse between two colors with delay/change of [t], which is optional (default is 20)

angry - You wouldn't like me when I'm angry

calm - chill man

partytime - rainbow o'clock

seizure - RAVE TIME

help - this message - though you probably knew that already since you got this message